      <description>&lt;p&gt;Had a great time visiting &lt;a href=&#34;https://fsuya.org/&#34;&gt;Professor Suya&lt;/a&gt; at the University of Tennessee, Knoxville.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I gave a talk (mostly on Hannah&amp;rsquo;s work, but also including some new work by Nia) in the &lt;a href=&#34;https://trustai-seminar.github.io/&#34;&gt;Tennessee RobUst, Secure, and Trustworthy AI Seminar&lt;/a&gt; (TRUST-AI) organized by Suya:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Tilting the BobbyTables and Steering the CensorShip&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://calendar.utk.edu/event/david-evans-uva-tilting-the-bobbytables-and-steering-the-censorship&#34;&gt;TRUST-AI Distinguished Seminar Seriesand Center for Social Theory&lt;/a&gt;. University of Tennessee, Knoxville. 27 March 2026.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;center&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;//uvasrg.github.io/images/utk2026/receivingaward.jpg&#34; width=&#34;85%&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/center&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;&lt;td width=&#34;42%&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;//uvasrg.github.io/images/utk2026/knoxvilleslide.jpg&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&lt;td width=&#34;50%&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;//uvasrg.github.io/images/utk2026/aftertalk.jpg&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;&lt;tr&gt;&#xA;&lt;td colspan=2&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;//uvasrg.github.io/images/utk2026/outsidehall.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;center&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/OnyHoque&#34;&gt;Ony Hoque&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://fsuya.org/&#34;&gt;Suya&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cs.virginia.edu/evans&#34;&gt;David Evans&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=&#34;https://sanskaramgain.com.np/&#34;&gt;Sanskar Amgain&lt;/a&gt; &#xA;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;</description>
